    {
        "content": "<p>I found this function but I don't know how to use this....</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Parser</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Command</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">#check</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">getDocStringText</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
