        "content": "<p>This does not work....</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">macro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"#doc\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"n\">ident</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">command</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">`</span><span class=\"o\">(</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">run_meta</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">some</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">findDocString</span><span class=\"bp\">?</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">getEnv</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">`</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">$</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">failure</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">logInfo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m</span><span class=\"bp\">!</span><span class=\"s2\">\"{s}\"</span>\n<span class=\"o\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">doc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">String</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
